data.description: Welcome to a vintage treasure that seamlessly blends modern farmhouse elegance in the sought-after Crescent Park neighborhood. Step into a world of upgrades, from the towering 12' ceilings to the inviting double-sided fireplace. Revel in the charm of plank flooring, a gas range, and updated electrical features. This home is move-in ready, offering a perfect blend of classic charm and contemporary convenience!
